 don't know why they're doing what they're doing or why they're there.

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:19.840
 A simple way to find that out is just sit down with each person individually

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:23.640
 and ask them, Why are you here? Don't be condescending when

00:00:23.640 --> 00:00:27.440
 you ask, obviously. But see if they actually understand what their

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:31.230
 purpose is. Why are they doing the job that they're doing? Why are

