 You'll find a lot of people really don't understand why they're doing

00:00:42.630 --> 00:00:46.430
 what they're doing, and you got to keep kind of probing and don't

00:00:46.430 --> 00:00:50.220
 take their first answer as the full one because it's more than likely

00:00:50.220 --> 00:00:54.020
 gonna be superficial. You might have to actually educate them on

00:00:54.020 --> 00:00:57.820
 why they're here and how they fit into the bigger picture. And once

00:00:57.820 --> 00:01:01.620
 they really understand that, and why that they're why they're doing

